window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Artificial intelligence/robotics: Have we opened a Pandoraâ€™s Box?&nbsp;</p> <p>As AI and robotics eliminate jobs across the spectrum, governmental revenues will plummet while the debt increases dramatically. This crisis of limited resources on all levels - underfunded or nonexistent pensions, health problems, lack of savings, and job destruction without comparable job creation - will drive many into homelessness and produce a dramatic rise in violence as we fight over shrinking resources.</p>"; 
